 applying our approach to twelve pooled samples from seven localities in Peru, we showed that detected viral communities saturated at the attained sequencing depth, allowing unbiased comparisons of viral community composition. Future studies using the methods outlined here will elucidate the determinants of viral communities across host species, environments and time.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Bergner, Laura M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Orton, Richard J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Da Silva Filipe, Ana", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Shaw, Andrew E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Becker, Daniel J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tello, Carlos", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Biek, Roman", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Streicker, Daniel G.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/f14c62c470fe091c98ca34c26eb021cf", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/94800dc2edea4f0a9715d0d2013c228ec15fbe3ee5217c867824388c45653bfe", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/I2T67GHP", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/I2T67GHP", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/ea119e42ba9146e290c5c36e27651dda!/b107381-109941", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article